    'description' => 'Cross-reference research from three independent sources: Wikipedia (via REST API), GitHub (via search API), and php.net (via RSS). Takes a search topic and returns structured data from all three sources with a consolidated summary. Uses http_fetch internally. Never throws — all errors returned as structured data. First-ever multi-API cross-reference tool in the ecosystem.',
    'parameters' => 
